snippet.title: Run Roo Run - Debut Trailer
snippet.description:
Famed games developer 5th Cell, creators of Scribblenauts, return with an original platforming Australian adventure "Run Roo Run." Players will follow Roo, a mother kangaroo in search of her kidnapped Joey. Check this game out on iPhone, iPad, and other iOS devices at the App Store for 99 cents. 

Hop over to IGN for more info:
http://wireless.ign.com/objects/126/126433.html

Subscribe to IGN's channel for reviews, news, and all things gaming:http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=ignentertainment
